CPC Central Committee Political Bureau: Implement congress' spirit
2012-11-17 00:28:12 GMT
The Political Bureau of the Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee held a meeting on Friday to arrange the implementation of the spirit of the just-concluded 18th CPC National Congress.The meeting was presided over by CPC Central Committee General Secretary Xi Jinping. The Party unveiled a new leadership lineup for the next five years Thursday.A statement released after the meeting described the 18th CPC National Congress, held from Nov. 8-14, as "an extremely important meeting convened at the decisive stage of completing the building of a moderately prosperous society in all respects."It went on to add that learning, promoting and implementing the congress's essence concerns the work of the Party and the country and the lasting development of the socialist cause with Chinese characteristics. It said this is of great realistic and historical significance in confidently completing the building of a moderately prosperous society in all respects and winning new victories of socialism with Chinese characteristics under the leadership of the CPC Central Committee with comrade Xi Jinping as the general secretary.The statement added that the foremost political task is to focus the minds of the Party, the nation and people of all ethnic backgrounds on the congress's spirit and meet the various tasks and goals that have been set forth in the congress. This will be done through learning, promoting and implementing the congress's spirit, the statement added.The meeting called for efforts to study the documents of the 18th CPC National Congress, including the work report of the 17th CPC Central Committee and the Party's Constitution.The meeting urged grasping the congress's significance, the historical achievements made by the CPC over the past five to ten years, the historical role and guiding significance of the Scientific Outlook on Development, the connotation of socialism with Chinese characteristics and the goal of completing the building of a moderately prosperous society and deepening reform and opening-up in all respects.It also urged deeply understanding socialist economic, political, cultural, social and ecological construction and the important task of promoting the scientific level of Party building.Officials and the masses should follow the spirit by intensifying training and publicity of the congress essence in enterprises, villages, government departments, schools and communities, the statement said.Learning the congress's spirit should be combined with the actual conditions of the work in respective regions and units, it said.The newly-amended CPC Constitution reflects the fruit of the Party's theoretical innovation and development of experimentation, important theories and views, guidelines and policies and work arrangements set by the congress and the requirements of adhering to and improving the CPC leadership and strengthening Party building, said the statement.The meeting called for diligently studying and strictly abiding by the CPC Constitution.
